---
title: Balsamic & Fig Beef Tenderloin with Garlic Mashed Potatoes & Rosemary Breadcrumb Brussels Sprouts
description: Gettin’ figgy with it! Fig jam, that is. Here, the sweet stuff is paired with balsamic vinegar to create a rich and tangy pan sauce for drizzling over beef tenderloin. Garlicky mashed potatoes are the perfect accompaniment for catching any extra sauce (and trust us, you won’t want to waste a drop.) Tender, caramelized Brussels sprouts join the mix, topped with crunchy, golden rosemary breadcrumbs. This dish is bursting with flavors and textures that’ll make your mouth dance.
